  <div id="text-content_b3b9d899-78e9-4388-b976-b40e42226a98" class="text-block-content">
    <p>View the events in your calendar. </p>
<p>Remember, once created, duplicate events are not linked together and are independent events. Therefore, if you need to modify an event, each event has to be edited individually.</p>
